snippet.title: Pineapple Smash Crew - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Lone game designer Rich Edwards and legendary chiptune artist Syphus teamed up, and the chaotic Pineapple Smash Crew was the result! Watch four adorable little soldiers smash through enemies in this new indie arcade shooter.

Release Date: February 02, 2012
MSRP: $9.99
Exclusively on: PC
Genre: Shooter 
Publisher: RichMakeGame
Developer: RichMakeGame

Grab your crew and head to IGN for more game info:
http://pc.ign.com/objects/128/128070.html

Subscribe to IGN's channel for reviews, guides, trailers and all things gaming: http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=ignentertainment
